Class PublicObjectiveCard

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2018.model.ObjectiveCard
      • it.polimi.se2018.model.PublicObjectiveCard
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DiagonalsPublicObjectiveCard, RowsColumnsPublicObjectiveCard, SetPublicObjectiveCard

    public abstract class PublicObjectiveCard
extends ObjectiveCard
    Represents Public Objective Cards as an abstract class that extends ObjectiveCard. Each Public Objective card has a property function to get a certain property of the dice in the windowPattern.
    Author:
    Jacopo Pio Gargano
